0x2B39128B.name: SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL

params.name: dirtLevel
params.description: A number between 0.0 and 15.0 representing the vehicles dirt level.

0x2B39128B.description:
Sets the dirt level of the passed vehicle.

**This is the server-side RPC native equivalent of the client native [SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL](?\_0x79D3B596FE44EE8B).**
